Regressin among all left-hemisphere ROIs for subject 481042¶

In [4]:
# NEO4J database call for GROUP 1 - Close and Connected
graph = Graph(password="1234")
c0 = '''MATCH (n:ROI)-[r:NOS]->(m:ROI)
WHERE r.weight < 1000 and n.hemisphere="L" and r.SUBJECT = 481042
RETURN n.name AS n1 ,m.name AS n2,r.length as D,r.weight as W,r._length as distance ,r._weight as weight, r.SUBJECT as subject
ORDER BY D'''

c1 = '''MATCH (n:ROI)-[r:NOS]->(m:ROI)
WHERE r.weight < 2500 and r.weight > 1000 and n.hemisphere="L" and r.SUBJECT = 481042
RETURN n.name AS n1 ,m.name AS n2,r.length as D,r.weight as W,r._length as distance ,r._weight as weight, r.SUBJECT as subject
ORDER BY D'''


c2 = '''MATCH (n:ROI)-[r:NOS]->(m:ROI)
WHERE r.weight > 2500 and n.hemisphere="L" and r.SUBJECT = 481042
RETURN n.name AS n1 ,m.name AS n2,r.length as D,r.weight as W,r._length as distance ,r._weight as weight, r.SUBJECT as subject
ORDER BY D'''

res = {}
for q,c in enumerate([c0,c1,c2]):
    A = graph.run(c)
    results = []
    for i,w in enumerate(A):
        a = np.array(w['distance'])
        b = np.array(w['weight'])
        D = regress_noplot(a,b)
        D['n1'] = w['n1']
        D['n2'] = w['n2']
        D['subject'] = w['subject']
        D['max-weight'] = w['W']
        D['distance'] = w['D']
        results.append(D)
    res[q] = [xx for xx in results]

Success rate and failure reasons¶

In [28]:
T = '''
---------------------------
Category:ZZZ
---------------------------
Number of pairs:AAA
Number of accepted Regressions:BBB
Rejected for R2:CCC
Rejected for Envelope:DDD
'''
cat = ['Weekly connected', 'Somewhat connected', 'strongly connected']
for q,K in enumerate(res):
    R = res[K]
    ZZZ = cat[q]
    AAA = len(R)
    BBB = len([xx for xx in R if xx['isSuccess']])
    CCC = len([xx for xx in R if (~xx['isSuccess'] and xx['reason']=='r2')])
    DDD = len([xx for xx in R if (~xx['isSuccess'] and xx['reason']=='envelope')])
    cur = T.replace('AAA',str(AAA)).replace('BBB',str(BBB)).replace('CCC',str(CCC)).replace('DDD',str(DDD)).replace('ZZZ',ZZZ)
    print(cur)

In [30]:
intercepts = [xx['intercept'] for xx in res[0] if (xx['isSuccess'])]
slopes = [xx['slope'] for xx in res[0] if (xx['isSuccess'])]



p1 = figure(title="Intercept weekly connected",tools="save",
            background_fill_color="#E8DDCB")


q1,q2 = np.percentile(intercepts,[2,98])

measured = [xx for xx in intercepts if (xx>q1 and xx<q2)]
hist, edges = np.histogram(measured, density=True, bins=50)


p1.quad(top=hist, bottom=0, left=edges[:-1], right=edges[1:],fill_color="#036564", line_color="#033649")


p1.legend.location = "center_right"
p1.legend.background_fill_color = "darkgrey"
p1.xaxis.axis_label = 'Intercept'
p1.yaxis.axis_label = 'Histpgram'



p2 = figure(title="Slopes weekly connected", tools="save",background_fill_color="#E8DDCB")


q1,q2 = np.percentile(slopes,[2,98])

measured = [xx for xx in slopes if (xx>q1 and xx<q2)]
hist, edges = np.histogram(measured, density=True, bins=50)


p2.quad(top=hist, bottom=0, left=edges[:-1], right=edges[1:],fill_color="#036564", line_color="#033649")

p2.legend.location = "center_right"
p2.legend.background_fill_color = "darkgrey"
p2.xaxis.axis_label = 'Slopes'
p2.yaxis.axis_label = 'Histogram'

In [32]:
suc = [xx for xx in res[0] if (xx["isSuccess"])]

l = len(suc)
P = {}
for i in range(8):
    k = randint(0,l-1)
    data = suc[k]
    title = D["n1"]+'->'+D["n2"]
    s = figure(plot_width=500, plot_height=500, title = title,y_axis_label = "Probability(log scale)",x_axis_label = "Distance")
    s.circle(data['a'],data['b'])
    x = [xx[0] for xx in data['envelope']]
    s.line(x,data['z'],legend="Regressor",color="red")
    mm = min(data['a'])
    mx = max(data['a'])
    s.line([mm,mx],[noise_floor,noise_floor],legend="noise floor",color="black")

    for v in data['envelope']:
            s.circle_cross(v[0],v[1],color='green',size=8)
    P[i] = s
